{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream\/init(data:size:reallocFunction:destroyFunction:)"},"abstract":[{"text":"Creates a new ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"init(data:size:reallocFunction:destroyFunction:)","symbolKind":"init","roleHeading":"Initializer","externalID":"s:3GIO18MemoryOutputStreamC4data4size15reallocFunction07destroyH0ACSvSg_SiA2H_SutXCSgyAHXCSgtcfc","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"size","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"reallocFunction"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GReallocFunc","text":"GReallocFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"destroyFunction"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"init"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"size","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reallocFunction","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GReallocFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GReallocFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"destroyFunction","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In most cases this is not the function you want.  See","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_memory_output_stream_new_resizable()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", the stream will use that for its internal storage."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"realloc_fn"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", it will be used for resizing the internal"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage when necessary and the stream will be considered resizable."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"In that case, the stream will start out being (conceptually) empty."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"size"},{"type":"text","text":" is used only as a hint for how big "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"type":"text","text":" is.  Specifically,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"seeking to the end of a newly-created stream will seek to zero, not","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"size"},{"text":".  Seeking past the end of the stream and then writing will","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"introduce a zero-filled gap."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"realloc_fn"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the stream is fixed-sized.  Seeking to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the end will seek to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"size"},{"type":"text","text":" exactly.  Writing past the end will give"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an ‘out of space’ error.  Attempting to seek past the end will fail."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Unlike the resizable case, seeking to an offset within the stream and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"writing will preserve the bytes passed in as ","type":"text"},{"code":"data","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" before that point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and will return them as part of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_memory_output_stream_steal_data()"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If you intend to seek you should probably therefore ensure that ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is properly initialised.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is probably only meaningful to provide "},{"code":"data","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"size"},{"type":"text","text":" in the case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that you want a fixed-sized stream.  Put another way: if ","type":"text"},{"code":"realloc_fn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" then it makes most sense to give ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"type":"text","text":" as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"size"},{"type":"text","text":" as 0 (allowing "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream"},{"text":" to do the initial","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allocation for itself)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ a stream that can grow","stream = g_memory_output_stream_new (NULL, 0, realloc, free);","","\/\/ another stream that can grow","stream2 = g_memory_output_stream_new (NULL, 0, g_realloc, g_free);","","\/\/ a fixed-size stream","data = malloc (200);","stream3 = g_memory_output_stream_new (data, 200, NULL, free);"],"syntax":"C"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/memoryoutputstream\/init(data:size:reallocfunction:destroyfunction:)"]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MemoryOutputStream/init(data:size:reallocFunction:destroyFunction:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream\/init(data:size:reallocFunction:destroyFunction:)","abstract":[{"text":"Creates a new ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/memoryoutputstream\/init(data:size:reallocfunction:destroyfunction:)","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"size","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reallocFunction","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GReallocFunc","text":"GReallocFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"text":"destroyFunction","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"title":"init(data:size:reallocFunction:destroyFunction:)","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/MemoryOutputStream":{"abstract":[{"code":"GMemoryOutputStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a class for using arbitrary"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"memory chunks as output for GIO streaming output operations."}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MemoryOutputStream","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/memoryoutputstream","title":"MemoryOutputStream","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MemoryOutputStream","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MemoryOutputStream","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}